Hi,

I'm handling 2 themes (one for dark mode) but mat-dialog, mat-datepicker, mat-option stay in dark theme.

#### Reproduction

[https://stackblitz.com/edit/components-issue-kn1w6o?file=src/app/example-component.html](https://stackblitz.com/edit/components-issue-kn1w6o?file=src/app/example-component.html)

_theme.scss_
```
@import '~@angular/material/theming';

@include mat-core();

$theme-primary: mat-palette($mat-blue);
$theme-accent:  mat-palette($mat-grey, A200, A100, A400);
$theme-warn:    mat-palette($mat-red);

$theme-light:   mat-light-theme($theme-primary, $theme-accent, $theme-warn);
$theme-dark:    mat-dark-theme($theme-primary, $theme-accent, $theme-warn);

@mixin cust-component($theme) {
  $background: map-get($theme, background);
  $primary: map-get($theme, primary);

  .mat-toolbar {
    background-color: mat-color($background, background);
    color: mat-color($primary, 500);
  }
}

.theme-light {
  @include angular-material-theme($theme-light);
  @include cust-component($theme-light);  
}

.theme-dark {
  @include angular-material-theme($theme-dark);
  @include cust-component($theme-dark);
}
```
_app.component.ts_
```
  private isDark = false;

  @HostBinding('class')
  get themeMode() {
    return this.isDark ? 'theme-dark' : 'theme-light';
  }

  toggleDarkMode() {
    this.isDark = !this.isDark;
    this.localstorageService.set('IS_DARK', this.isDark);
  }

  constructor(
    overlayContainer: OverlayContainer) {}
```

#### Expected Behavior

mat-datetime, mat-dialog, and mat-option from mat-select are supposed to change depending on theme choosed.

#### Actual Behavior

mat-dialog, mat-option, mat-datetime background is everytime using dark theme. 
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/41122476/91544285-cc5b1280-e91f-11ea-9567-b3500509cec0.png)


![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/41122476/91541554-ce6fa200-e91c-11ea-951f-7105a22b44a4.png)
`cdk-overlay-container` isn't changing theme
but `app-root` do.

#### Environment

- Angular Angular Material
